thorities) regulations 2017 which came into force on 31 March 2017.  These regulations underpin the Public Sector Equality Duty and require relevant organisations to publish their gender pay gap by 4 April 2018.  NTW Solutions has published their gender pay information today.          Categories      Announcements    Awards    Blogs    Campaigns    Newsletter    Publications    Research    Training    Uncategorized          Archive     April 2018  March 2018  February 2018  January 2018  December 2017  November 2017  October 2017  September 2017  August 2017  July 2017  June 2017  May 2017                       Northumberland, Tyne and Wear NHS Foundation Trust  St. Nicholas Hospital  Jubilee Road  Gosforth  Newcastle upon Tyne  NE3 3XT         0191 246 6800       Facebook  LinkedIn  Twitter  Youtube  WordPress                  Freedom of Information  Contact  Help  Translation      © Copyright 2017-2018 Northumberland, Tyne and Wear NHS Foundation Trust  Lovingly crafted by Mixd            